<span id="freeTextContainer12327158316611093071"><strong>Another well-crafted story! </strong><br/><br/>I flew through this book. Loved the characters and the plot line zags and zags that I wasn’t expecting. I look forward to the next book in this series!! <br/><br/>If you liked A Discovery of Witches trilogy by Deborah Harkness, I think you would enjoy this series. </span>

