  <span id="freeText17126507347877017847" style="display:none"><strong>A page turner!</strong><br /><br />The author truly develops her character for the reader as well as the story. I truly had enjoyed the Immortals and that made choosing the sequel a nobrainer. Often a series book can be disappointing, this held my interest as much as the first. The sights, sounds and history seem so real. I have a hard time writing about a book that I enjoy because I do not wish to spoil the many twists and turns of this detail-rich novel for someone who has yet to read it. Let me say this; I anxiously await the next book! </span>
