<span id="freeTextContainer1855682358088912418"><strong>More adventures with the Ancient Family</strong><br/><br/>We met them in the first book and this one takes us further into their history and ours. Some new villains are introduced and dealt with, too. A bunch of editing errors, but who cares when the story is this good?!</span>

