  <span id="freeText10506333004097692525" style="display:none">I´m continuing to enjoy the story of the family of ancients and the "ephemera" (ie: someone who will live a normal lifetime) one of them married. The tension continues between the brother who wants to figure out how to make other people long livers, and the rest of the family, and starts out with the kidnapping of the mortal wife in order to blackmail her husband into reversing the shot he gave her kidnapper to reverse his immortality. Meanwhile, the history of the family continues to unfold revealing another family of long livers who are the sworn enemy of the family. There are still a lot of unanswered questions at the end, so hopefully there will be another volume in the series eventually. There were still some translation and editing problems, but I was able to overlook them. </span>
